    feat: add correlation analysis, orphan detection, ML baselines to Dev tab
    
    Health Map panel now includes:
      - Root Cause Analysis: when drilling into a broken component, shows
        upstream root causes vs downstream cascade effects, with plain
        English diagnosis and alert suppression for leaf failures
      - Detect Orphans button: finds services that are alive but unused
      - Learn Baselines button: analyzes 7 days of Genesis key history
        to show each component's natural rhythm, configured vs recommended
        intervals, peak hours ΓÇö in a comparison table
      - All integrated into the drill-down flow
    
    Co-authored-by: aaron031291 <aaron031291@users.noreply.github.com>
